    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "### Problem\n\nWith inlay hints enabled in insert mode, the cursor jumps when an inlay hint left of the cursor is updated, which is irritating.\n\nWith inlay hints toggled off in insert mode, the whole file \"changes\", which is also irritating.\n\n### Expected behavior\n\nDisable inlay hints **only** in the cursor line when entering insert mode.",
